DialogueText:
Patient:
Hey there I have had cold "symptoms" for over a week and had a low grade fever last week. For the past two days I have been feeling dizzy. Should I contact my dr? See a dr?
Doctor:
Dizziness. Yes. Please contact your doctor since they know you better. He may want to test you for the virus. There are other reasons you may be dizzy as well. .
